{"tid":32311,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺D MK仔操到幾舊腹肌就當正自己好撚Fit好勁?!","createTime":"2016-12-10T06:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T12:58:29.000Z","uid":20637,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"20bddba997240cdd15f50d2f4592214568e9ca7a","tid":32311,"uid":20637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:13:55.000Z","msg":"想當年我仲讀緊BAND 3中學<br />\n<br />\n有條MK狗係咁話我, 話約我隻揪<br />\n<br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好撚好打<br />\n<br />\n(但其實我當時己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉<br />\n<br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型<br />\n<br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎)<br />\n<br />\n我D 毒向左走向右走FD 嚇撚到標尿<br />\n<br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」<br />\n<br />\n「你癡左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」<br />\n<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲<br />\n<br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量<br />\n<br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間<br />\n<br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇<br />\n<br />\n佢就除左件校服<br />\n<br />\n成個小醜咁係到穀佢果幾舊腹肌仔<br />\n<br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後佢打到我Hi Hi, 牙都甩埋<br />\n<br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關"},{"pid":"d076384f8020c59585e4ca0de797995209d572a0","tid":32311,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:25:48.000Z","msg":"恥笑開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4362beebe0b77e2d8f579156149b9a74304355a3","tid":32311,"uid":59955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T06:27:20.000Z","msg":"又幾好笑"},{"pid":"4a3c9e7becebdbf7d5a21c3d2511f05a274a0127","tid":32311,"uid":41975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy